- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a possibility as the paper mentions repairing null dereferences, which can be a security vulnerability.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as the paper uses bandit algorithms, which are a type of online machine learning algorithm.
